main event: A UFO was reported in Rolla, Missouri, on 4 October 1965, described as a steady white light moving northeast.
interesting points: The object was observed traveling steadily without blinking at 1942,The object was concluded to be a satellite,The sighting was noted to have no physical evidence,There are claims that the object did not fit the characteristics of known satellites or space probes,The report expressed concerns regarding government secrecy around UFO phenomena.
witness description: No witness descriptions were provided in the report.
